 "unit": "7 — Quadratic Functions & Equations",
 "description": "The student can solve a quadratic by factoring, confirm roots with the quadratic formula, and translate a real-world quadratic constraint from a word problem into a correctly structured equation before solving. All 6 diagnostic laws active simultaneously. The terminal full-sensor artifact.\n",
 "unlock_condition": "mastery >= 0.8 on all required skills, confirmed by boss challenge",
